## title

### Source (en)

~~~text
Could pseudonymization be used to make the data more openly available?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
是否可以透過假名化（pseudonymization）使資料更加公開可用？
~~~

## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
Legally, pseudonymous data (which means that someone has the key to reverse the process) is still considered privacy sensitive information. However, the EU is working on special cases where the data can still be opened as long as the key availability is sufficiently limited.
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
從法律上來說，假名化資料（也就是仍有人持有可將該處理過程還原之金鑰的資料）仍被視為隱私敏感資訊。不過，歐盟目前正研議某些特殊情況，只要該金鑰的可取得性受到充分限制，這類資料仍可能可以開放。
~~~
